 itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:50.850" end="1:51.070">そ</span><span begin="1:51.070" end="1:51.200">れ</span><span begin="1:51.200" end="1:51.480">は</span><span begin="1:51.480" end="1:51.800">恋</span><span begin="1:51.800" end="1:51.980">だ</span><span begin="1:51.980" end="1:52.130">っ</span><span begin="1:52.130" end="1:52.330">た</span><span begin="1:52.330" end="1:52.710">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那可能是恋爱</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore wa koi dattari</span></p><p begin="1:52.440" end="1:53.550" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.440" end="1:52.900">涙</span><span begin="1:52.900" end="1:53.080">だ</span><span begin="1:53.080" end="1:53.220">っ</span><span begin="1:53.220" end="1:53.380">た</span><span begin="1:53.380" end="1:53.550">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可能是眼泪</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namida dattari</span></p><p begin="1:53.310" end="1:54.650" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:53.310" end="1:53.800">薬</span><span begin="1:53.800" end="1:53.980">だ</span><span begin="1:53.980" end="1:54.100">っ</span><span begin="1:54.100" end="1:54.250">た</span><span begin="1:54.250" end="1:54.650">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可能是良药</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kusuri dattari</span></p><p begin="1:54.500" end="1:56.380" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.500" end="1:54.750">そ</span><span begin="1:54.750" end="1:54.890">れ</span><span begin="1:54.890" end="1:55.170">は</span><span begin="1:55.170" end="1:55.680">絆</span><span begin="1:55.680" end="1:55.830">だ</span><span begin="1:55.830" end="1:55.940">っ</span><span begin="1:55.940" end="1:56.120">た</span><span begin="1:56.120" end="1:56.380">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那可能是羁绊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore wa kizuna dattari</span></p><p begin="1:55.940" end="1:57.340" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:55.940" end="1:56.580">唇</span><s