="2:53.660">ら</span><span begin="2:53.660" end="2:53.950">ら</span> <span begin="2:53.950" end="2:54.510">ら</span><span begin="2:54.510" end="2:54.830">ら</span><span begin="2:54.830" end="2:55.770">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啦啦啦 啦啦 啦啦 啦啦啦</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Rarara rara rara rarara</span></p><p begin="3:01.540" end="3:06.710" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:01.540" end="3:01.880">音</span><span begin="3:01.880" end="3:02.490">楽</span><span begin="3:02.490" end="3:02.780">は</span><span begin="3:02.780" end="3:03.120">魔</span><span begin="3:03.120" end="3:06.710">法</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">音乐即是魔法</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ongaku wa mahou</span></p></div></body></tt>